{"tid":1179698,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《God Help The Girl / 戀戀小情歌》","createTime":"2019-05-31T09:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T08:34:50.000Z","uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"612dab3d58ebaaf080b297568910b73c01cb598a","tid":1179698,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1. 劇情大意</div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m21.hk/filmblog/2014/10/god-help-the-girl-review-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm21.hk%2Ffilmblog%2F2014%2F10%2Fgod-help-the-girl-review-2%2F&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoBs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=fcd60adf\" target=\"_blank\">https://m21.hk/filmblog/2014/10/god-help-the-girl-review-2/</a><br />\n<em>主角Eve因情緒問題和厭食症長期在一所醫院接受治療。對她而言，醫院是拘禁病人的場所，所以她三番四次偷偷地逃出去，想像正常人般生活。在機緣巧合下，Eve遇上結他手James和天真爛慢的Cass。三個人透過音樂在迷惘中尋找生命的旋律，在徘徊與不安之間找到屬於自己理想和信念。</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2. 結果</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><em>悠長又短暫的暑假過後，Eve選擇前往倫敦讀音樂，James繼續留在自己的小城市，而Cass還是像孩子般無憂無慮。</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3. 相關</div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com.hk/lifestyle/culture/god-help-the-girl-2014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.harpersbazaar.com.hk%2Flifestyle%2Fculture%2Fgod-help-the-girl-2014&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoBs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=20f86e0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.harpersbazaar.com.hk/lifestyle/culture/god-help-the-girl-2014</a><br />\n<em>說 Indie Pop 名團 Belle &amp; Sebastian 是當代蘇格蘭最具代表性的樂團，相信無人反對，不止曲子清新可喜，正如朋友都說他們的歌詞實在很適合女孩子；近日團中 frontman 兼主唱 Stuart Murdoch 籌備經年，首次自編自導的大銀幕電影《戀戀小情歌》（God Help the Girl），在各地影展上受到熱烈迴響，大放異彩，令 Indie 樂迷為之鼓舞！</em><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9J30NEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9J30NEP.jpg&h=dd61d5d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭文青獨立流行名團 Belle &amp; Sebastian 轉捩點專輯20週年<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%89%AD%E8%80%B3%E4%BB%94/232909/%E8%98%87%E6%A0%BC%E8%98%AD%E6%96%87%E9%9D%92%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%90%8D%E5%9C%98-belle-sebastian-%E8%BD%89%E6%8D%A9%E9%BB%9E%E5%B0%88%E8%BC%AF20%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2589%25AD%25E8%2580%25B3%25E4%25BB%2594%2F232909%2F%25E8%2598%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E8%2598%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E9%259D%2592%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%259C%2598-belle-sebastian-%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%258D%25A9%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25BC%25AF20%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%25B9%25B4&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoBs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=63a53a6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%89%AD%E8%80%B3%E4%BB%94/232909/%E8%98%87%E6%A0%BC%E8%98%AD%E6%96%87%E9%9D%92%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%90%8D%E5%9C%98-belle-sebastian-%E8%BD%89%E6%8D%A9%E9%BB%9E%E5%B0%88%E8%BC%AF20%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">4. 其他</div><br />\n<br />\n《戀戀小情歌》青春是唱歌和跳舞<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.filmcritics.org.hk/film-review/node/2015/08/07/%E3%80%8A%E6%88%80%E6%88%80%E5%B0%8F%E6%83%85%E6%AD%8C%E3%80%8B%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%94%B1%E6%AD%8C%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%B3%E8%88%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.filmcritics.org.hk%2Ffilm-review%2Fnode%2F2015%2F08%2F07%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%2588%2580%25E6%2588%2580%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25AD%258C%25E3%2580%258B%25E9%259D%2592%25E6%2598%25A5%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2594%25B1%25E6%25AD%258C%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E8%2588%259E&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoBs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=abc9227b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.filmcritics.org.hk/film-review/node/2015/08/07/%E3%80%8A%E6%88%80%E6%88%80%E5%B0%8F%E6%83%85%E6%AD%8C%E3%80%8B%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%94%B1%E6%AD%8C%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%B3%E8%88%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n《戀戀小情歌》（God Help the Girl）：一首屬於青春的歌<br />\n<a href=\"http://chingszechuen.blogspot.com/2014/11/god-help-the-girl.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchingszechuen.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F11%2Fgod-help-the-girl.html&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoBs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=bcd1ad45\" target=\"_blank\">http://chingszechuen.blogspot.com/2014/11/god-help-the-girl.html</a><br />\n<br />\n《戀夏小情歌》（God Help the Girl）&mdash;&mdash; 用耳朵聽的復古穿搭學<br />\n<a href=\"https://flipermag.com/2014/10/07/god-help-the-girl/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflipermag.com%2F2014%2F10%2F07%2Fgod-help-the-girl%2F&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoBs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=d1377946\" target=\"_blank\">https://flipermag.com/2014/10/07/god-help-the-girl/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">5. 睇後感？</div><br />\n<br />\ni<br />\n望住James，覺得自己有d似佢。<br />\n記得有幕，佢好似俾女主角類似話：<br />\n你咁女性化既男仔唔會成功。<br />\n<br />\n到最後，女主角同另一隊Band既男仔一齊過。<br />\nJames就只係一次又一次錯過機會。<br />\n<br />\nii<br />\n睇完，望返電影名：God Help The Girl。<br />\n諗起女主講&hellip;嗰個Christian療法？<br />\n治療者既手，離身地掃患者既身。<br />\n女主作為患者，先無感覺，後有夢，然後感覺幾日狀態好差，然後好返，覺得係個排毒過程。<br />\n似Placebo effect、安慰劑效應？<br />\n<br />\n成個暑假，就係神帶俾女主既排毒過程？<br />\n<br />\n神唔存在。<br />\n治療唔存在。<br />\n只係患者本身，同佢既信念，令治療效果出現。<br />\n<br />\nBand存在。<br />\nBand無治療效果。<br />\n夾Band過程，俾男友將自己既音樂踐踏過後，認清現實。<br />\n自我中心Narcissism係毒。<br />\n厭食係毒。<br />\n唔迎合大眾主流係毒。<br />\n夾Band過程，加上過程中既唔同經驗，造成排毒。<br />\n<br />\n然後女主就去College正式學音樂，擁抱主流。<br />\n<br />\niii <br />\nIndie pop，對自己既生活經驗，看似輕易配樂、填詞，將生活經驗轉為一種可以留低、自己或他人享受既藝術作品。<br />\n好羨慕呢種能力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">6. 你呢？睇過有咩感想或睇法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"86424f7221b0148f52f2176b9ac74488a93ccf55","tid":1179698,"uid":34132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"幾年前係戲院睇左 已經唔記得哂啲劇情<br />\n淨係知soundtrack好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa